      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The cost of government",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 3.66,
      "endTime": 11.15
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What's the most important factor, both in government or business, for keeping running costs low?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 11.16,
      "endTime": 21.56
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "If a nation is essentialy disunited, it is left to the government to hold it together.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 21.57,
      "endTime": 27.96,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This increases the expense of government, and reduces correspondingly the amount of economic resources that could be used for developing the country.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 27.97,
      "endTime": 39.41,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "And it should not be forgotten how small those resources are in a poor and backward country.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.42,
      "endTime": 45.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "How",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "怎样，如何"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Where the cost of government is high, resources for development are correspondingly low.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 45.74,
      "endTime": 52.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "This may be illustrated by comparing the position of a nation with that of a private business enterprise.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 52.66,
      "endTime": 59.83,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "An enterprise has to incur certain costs and expenses in order to stay in business.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 59.84,
      "endTime": 66.87
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "For our purposes, we are concerned only with one kind of cost--the cost of managing and administering the business.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.88,
      "endTime": 75.35,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Such administrative overheads in a business are analogous to the cost of government in a nation.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.36,
      "endTime": 82.52,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The administrative overheads of a business are low to the extent that everyone working in the business",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.53,
      "endTime": 88.2,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "can be trusted to behave in a way that best promotes the interests of the firm.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.21,
      "endTime": 94.05,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "If they can each be trusted to take such responsibilities,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 94.06,
      "endTime": 97.78,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and to exercise such initiative as falls within their sphere, then administrative overheads will be low.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 97.79,
      "endTime": 106.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It will be low because it will be necessary to have only one man looking after each job without having another man to check upon what he is doing,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 106.41,
      "endTime": 116.05,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          },
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "keep him in line, and report on him to someone else.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 116.06,
      "endTime": 120.58
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But if no one can be trusted to act in a loyal and responsible manner towards his job,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 120.59,
      "endTime": 126.87,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "then the business will require armies of administrators, checkers and foremen and administrative overheads will rise correspondingly.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 126.88,
      "endTime": 136.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "As administrative overheads rise, so the earnings of the business after meeting the expense of administration, will fall;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 136.66,
      "endTime": 144.75,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and the business will have less money to distribute as dividends or invest directly in its future progress and development.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 144.76,
      "endTime": 152.85,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It is precisely the same with a nation.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 152.86,
      "endTime": 156.05,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "To the extent that the people can be relied on to behave in a loyal and responsible manner,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 156.06,
      "endTime": 162.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the government does not require armies of police and civil servants to keep them in order.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 162.17,
      "endTime": 168.59,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But if a nation is disunited, the government cannot be sure that the actions of the people will be in the interests of the nation;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 168.6,
      "endTime": 177.2,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and it will have to watch, check, and control the people accordingly.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 177.21,
      "endTime": 182.35,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "A disunited nation therefore has to incur unduly high costs of government.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 182.36,
      "endTime": 187.36
    }
  ]
}
